      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PRESSURE POINT (4) scored well last start as odds-on favourite by a nose at this track in a handy 18.03 beating Speechless. Awkwardly drawn but likes the trip. Well placed and can measure up. SHANNY ROSE (8) drew a squeeze box and was game in defeat when a close third, 1.75 lengths from the winner ROUGH BOY ROCKY (18.24) at this track. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings two times from four attempts. Leading chance. ROUGH BOY ROCKY (6) took the sit on the lead from an outside box but levelled up and drew clear to score (18.11) at this track in a TG1-4W over 305m. Yet to score from this box but has never missed the frame in two starts. Will go close again if runs up to latest. SENIOR CITIZEN (1) can sneak into the finish with the right run.",
